                            <comment id="12762516" author="adeneche" created="Tue, 6 Oct 2009 06:36:20 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;I tested the change on the following examples:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&apos;.clustering.syntheticcontrol...&apos;:
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;before the patch &apos;dirichlet&apos; and &apos;kmeans&apos; had the CNF exception&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;after the patch &apos;dirichlet&apos; is getting a java.io.IOException: Cannot open filename /user/hadoop/output/state/state-3/_logs, but I suppose this is another story. The other examples did not throw any exception.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
