	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;the examples that I didn&apos;t test are &apos;cf.taste...&apos; and &apos;classifier.bayes...&apos;. Actually I tried but they seem a little complicated to run- for a complete Noob like me =P&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
